        <abstract> 
<p>Asks her to see whether the flowers or leaves of <hi rend="italic">Erica massoni</hi> are noted as glutinous in the <hi rend="italic">Botanical Magazine</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Inquires about the pods of peony: are they brilliantly coloured and do birds eat them?</p>
